title: Resolution RE concurrence to the House of Assembly on the amendments to Merchant Shipping Bill, 2024
markdown:
RESOLUTION NO.

HOUSE OF ASSEMBLY

BE IT RESOLVED that the Honourable the House of Assembly concur in the

amendments made by the Honourable the Senate to the Merchant Shipping Bill,

2024.

2024.

APPROVED by the House of Assembly this          day of                                      ,

Speaker
